00:52:24.560 --> 00:52:30.000
We kind of have two phases, two large phases to our project process

00:52:30.159 --> 00:52:35.439
where the first phase, which we can kind of promise to our end-users that come to us

00:52:35.439 --> 00:52:40.959
is that we'll do the diligence, explore the data, assess feasibility of modeling.

00:52:40.959 --> 00:52:46.959
But if we end at that point and just find that there's not enough data to build a predictive model,

00:52:46.959 --> 00:52:49.679
