00:54:18.000 --> 00:54:19.679
So we don't have, like, a singular metric.

00:54:20.000 --> 00:54:25.520
In many cases, a lot of, like, the predictive algorithms are,

00:54:26.399 --> 00:54:28.800
it's very important to have good,

00:54:32.719 --> 00:54:37.120
good, basically good performance to avoid, like, false negatives,

00:54:37.679 --> 00:54:41.040
