00:54:41.040 --> 00:54:43.280
So we'll focus on, like, PPV and NPV,

00:54:43.919 --> 00:54:47.280
or false positive, true positive, false negative rates.

00:54:47.840 --> 00:54:50.320
But there's no singular way of doing this.

00:54:51.120 --> 00:54:56.959
